headline: Get All the Tools for Back to School at Kroger
summary: The Kroger Co. (NYSE: KR) today shared Big Deal! back-to-school savings as students prepare to head back to the lunchroom and low prices on classroom supplies starting at just 39 cents. New this year, the retailer is debuting the Kroger Back to School List, an online tool offering supply lists issued by teachers from local schools across America. Customers can find their child's approved supply list and add it to their cart to get crayons, notebooks and more alongside their lunch and fresh groce
